# Look at Camera
Rotates your model's eyes towards the camera.
Credit to [Yarny](https://bsky.app/profile/yarny.land) as this came about from a conversation with her and a related setup she was trying

### Alternative Version: Nudge Eyes 2 Camera
Slight modification of the Look-At-Camera and what I personally run for myself. Allows for eyes to just be nudged by some amount to the camera with limits, so it's more natural and lets your eyes otherwise still move around.

## Instructions
Copy either of the code blocks below or in the text file and import it a graph

![example image](look-at-camera.png "Look at graph example")

### Look At Block
```
VNYANGRAPH:
```
